  "2026-07-23T10:17:49.204Z",codex-root,"Duplicate check 2026-07-23: all-status searches for relationship snapshot timestamp, offline late event, out-of-order event-time, and point-in-time relationship reads found the closed relationship platform pm-ju83, the active digital-twin exemplar pm-kr3t, and generic event-stream/federation items, but no item tracking this exact append-prefix correctness defect."
  "2026-07-23T11:18:50.935Z",codex-root,"TDD evidence: the regression appends future event-time data before late/offline historical data, supersedes and removes relationships, and asserts point-in-time snapshots select all events at or before the boundary while retaining the highest included append sequence. Focused tests and the 6129-test 100% coverage suite pass."
